{"tid":954169,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屢為港發聲　艾思定男爵病逝","createTime":"2018-12-24T12:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T17:19:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c334c3d983d76d9f3bc84bfbf192944ef2871a9b","tid":954169,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:03:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181224/20575590\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F20575590&d=R7iPOJPSqF%2BL1M6bNGf3SeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=64db2f03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181224%2F20575590&h=3a96f070\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181224/20575590</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月24日 <br />\n屢為港發聲　艾思定男爵病逝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181224/large/24la7p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181224%2Flarge%2F24la7p5.jpg&h=8a28225b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n艾思定男爵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一直關注香港前途發展的英國自由民主黨前黨魁艾思定男爵（Paddy Ashdown）周六病逝，終年77歲，他今年10月被確診患膀胱癌，相隔兩個月後離世，英國首相文翠珊與多位前首相都發聲明致哀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指持BNO港人應有居英權<br />\n<br />\n艾思定現為英國人權組織「香港監察」贊助人，去年訪港時曾指英國政府應給予持有英國公民（海外）護照（BNO）的港人有居英權。香港監察發聲明形容艾思定是港人的朋友，一直為香港民主、法治、人權及自治發聲；其所屬政黨讚揚他一生為推動自由主義作出不可估量的貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n艾思定曾是英軍突擊隊員，1983年當選國會議員，1988年成為自民黨黨魁，之後11年領導該黨成為英國政壇的新興力量，挑戰保守黨與工黨的雙寡頭壟斷形勢。他去年訪港時除提及居英權問題，亦談及敏感議題，包括銅鑼灣書店一事，認為書商若因敏感書籍被綁架到大陸，嚴重削弱市民對法治及言論自由的信心，又質疑有熱誠的「雙學三子」被判囚是否明智之舉，強調特區政府有責任捍衞香港的特殊地位和核心價值。 <br />\n<br />\n人民力量立法會議員陳志全去年曾與艾思定有一面之緣，陳對其BNO言論印象深刻，讚揚對方在港人BNO平權運動上「站在最前線」；又稱對方公開支持議會抗爭，肯定了「拉布」的價值，認為「對時間的運用，是在民主制度下，反對派唯一的武器」，稱對艾思定的支持與鼓勵銘記於心。<br />\n■記者許偉賢  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n變相多一層　丁屋申建太陽能板急增<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n壹週刊：緊閉大宅變藝術天地　李明哲音樂激活虎豹別墅"},{"pid":"85fbe23626820525552f4ec3e7f022f872809cb7","tid":954169,"uid":141862,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:04:53.000Z","msg":"R.I.P.<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c17d16fc03f3113edc759cc965a6c63653ed2fb","tid":954169,"uid":120070,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c50089d45d60862850326eff067328c1f77e2b1","tid":954169,"uid":126731,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"RIP. <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5cd469edd0dc20b8d962194dc54cb9aa8eab2d3","tid":954169,"uid":7107,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"佢讚成俾BNO腥港人有居英權，D偽善英國鬼內心一定好憎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca359bdad0987590f27c881f59ba4ea3518282c","tid":954169,"uid":171866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43209fba9dd6590169858eb59e74468e756445e1","tid":954169,"uid":189160,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d5cd469edd0dc20b8d962194dc54cb9aa8eab2d3","tid":954169,"uid":7107,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:16:03.000Z","msg":"佢讚成俾BNO腥港人有居英權，D偽善英國鬼內心一定好憎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:31:44.000Z","msg":"香港人反大陸人黎<br />\n英國唔可以反你班港支黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"dd3d3cc2ec05785fff9b18cda1c6d867195a41ee","tid":